author: dlr
msg: * STATUS
Cast some votes.  Regarding r14580, MSDN says:
CRYPTPROTECT_UI_FORBIDDEN:
This flag is used for remote situations where presenting a user
interface (UI) is not an option. When this flag is set and a UI is
specified for either protection or unprotection, the call fails and
GetLastError() returns the ERROR_PASSWORD_RESTRICTION status code.
